FURTHER READING
* David Camp , " The Cat 's Meow :
Martin Short has never carried a hit movie or a long - running sitcom .
Early on , he despaired at being left behind by friends such as Paul Shaffer , Gilda Radner , and Bill Murray .
But at 62 he stands alone in the comedy firmament , adored by Hollywood 's elite as the funniest , nicest , best of them all , " Vanity Fair , January 2013 .
